# HalalWatch
A chromium extension designed to keep you on track with your halal lifestyle! Simply define websites that contains halal/haram content and see it again by clicking the extension icon.

## Adding Halal/Haram Content To The List

<img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="" />

If the page you are visiting is classified as Unmoderated, simply click the report button and fill in the details! This will classify the website you filled in as what you classified (It will only be stored on your local device for now).
